query:
SELECT 
  brand,
  COUNT(*) as total_products,
  SUM(CASE WHEN detailedDescription IS NOT NULL AND detailedDescription != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_description,
  SUM(CASE WHEN particleSize IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_particle_size,
  SUM(CASE WHEN poreSize IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_pore_size,
  SUM(CASE WHEN columnLength IS NOT NULL AND innerDiameter IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_dimensions,
  SUM(CASE WHEN phRange IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_ph_range
FROM products
GROUP BY brand
ORDER BY brand
